ank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/</a><br />\n7.21 警察現場發放多枚催淚彈 22:20 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F450544468858025%2F&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=e2922c13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/</a><br />\n速龍小隊斥記者「係咪中立、係咪有立場」Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F631475204017598%2F&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=cfbcbbb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/</a><br />\n【7.21 現場】警察防線前的媽媽 Stand News 立場新聞 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F679125395894103%2F&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=d34aefa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/</a><br />\n【721開槍實錄】 克警濫暴，我們必定會追究到底。 林鄭，請爲每滴港人流的血負責。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2Fvideos%2F583308962199292%2F&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ab6d6cc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/</a><br />\n2019.07.21【中聯辦外示威者發表宣言】斥政府冷漠面對民間訴求 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDZ6SZIliQA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVDZ6SZIliQA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=3816aa79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VDZ6SZIliQA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n20190721 10:59 臨時街停車場 對出 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgF3afU7NSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEgF3afU7NSY&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=3df424d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EgF3afU7NSY</a><br />\n20190721 10:20PM 信德中心 天橋 對出 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KSn1vhTunl8&amp;t=7s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKSn1vhTunl8%26t%3D7s&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=14930f15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KSn1vhTunl8&amp;t=7s</a><br />\n警方在上環驅散示威者 多次施放催淚彈和發射橡膠子彈 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VKI-jSfhiO0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVKI-jSfhiO0&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=1f7f6a1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VKI-jSfhiO0</a><br />\n警方周日晚在上環採取行動驅散示威者 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KAnjB-Q8QV0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKAnjB-Q8QV0&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=25c86abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KAnjB-Q8QV0</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n上環backup : 多謝巴打 - 香城落雨聲 <br />\n(721)( 22:20)警察現場發放多枚催淚彈(立場) <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/nzv3gd9a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fnzv3gd9a&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=ec3a70e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/nzv3gd9a</a> <br />\n(721)上環黑警開槍實錄 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/vq65o7mx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fvq65o7mx&d=DQhhZyJ%2BQntsVA7gHYVTWAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=7948248c\" data-au